    "license": "IPIP items are in the public domain (ipip.ori.org: \"The IPIP items are in the public domain\"). 98 of the 100 BFAS items are public-domain IPIP items — this includes 2 items that are reverse-wordings of IPIP items (\"Avoid imposing my will on others.\" = reverse of IPIP H721 \"Impose my will on others.\"; \"Rarely put people under pressure.\" = reverse of IPIP H774 \"Put people under pressure.\"). 2 of the 100 items are NOT public-domain IPIP: (1) \"Am not a very enthusiastic person.\" was newly written for the BFAS by DeYoung et al. (copyright authors; distributed freely for research); (2) \"Do not have an assertive personality.\" is a reverse-wording of an item from the Big Five Inventory (John, Naumann & Soto, 2008), which is copyrighted but free for non-commercial research use. The assembled 100-item BFAS is freely usable for non-commercial research.",
    "license_class": "public_domain",
